Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.utils.indexings

Class BasicVarIndexing

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.core.utils.indexings.BasicVarIndexing
All Implemented Interfaces:
VarIndexing
public class BasicVarIndexing extends Object implements VarIndexing
Represents an immutable mapping, where each variable is associated with an index. The inner builder class can also be used to create a new instance.
